### Dossier Registry API - Local Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000 (default Vercel dev port)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/health

###

### List All Dossiers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dossiers

###

### Get Dossier Metadata
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dossiers/getting-started/hello

###

### Get Dossier Content (302 Redirect to CDN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dossiers/getting-started/hello/content

###

### 404 - Dossier Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dossiers/nonexistent/dossier

###

### 404 - Nested path not found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dossiers/some/deep/nested/path

###

### ========================================
### Authentication Tests
### ========================================

### Get Current User - No Token (should return 401 MISSING_TOKEN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/me

###

### Get Current User - Invalid Token (should return 401 INVALID_TOKEN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/me
Authorization: Bearer invalid.token.here

###

### Get Current User - Valid Token
# Replace <JWT> with actual token from OAuth flow
# GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/me
# Authorization: Bearer <JWT>

###

### OAuth Callback - Missing Code (should return error page)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/callback

###

### OAuth Callback - With Test Code (will fail but tests routing)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/callback?code=test_code

###

### ========================================
### Publish Tests
### ========================================

### Publish Dossier - No Token (should return 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dossiers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "namespace": "yuvaldim/test",
  "content": "---\nname: my-dossier\ntitle: My Dossier\nversion: 1.0.0\n---\n\n# Hello",
  "changelog": "Initial publish"
}

###

### Publish Dossier - Missing namespace (should return 400)
# POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dossiers
# Content-Type: application/json
# Authorization: Bearer <JWT>
#
# {
#   "content": "---\nname: my-dossier\ntitle: My Dossier\nversion: 1.0.0\n---\n\n# Hello"
# }

###

### Publish Dossier - Invalid frontmatter (should return 400)
# POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dossiers
# Content-Type: application/json
# Authorization: Bearer <JWT>
#
# {
#   "namespace": "yuvaldim/test",
#   "content": "# No frontmatter here"
# }

###

### Publish Dossier - Wrong namespace (should return 403)
# POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dossiers
# Content-Type: application/json
# Authorization: Bearer <JWT>
#
# {
#   "namespace": "someone-else/test",
#   "content": "---\nname: my-dossier\ntitle: My Dossier\nversion: 1.0.0\n---\n\n# Hello"
# }

###

### Publish Dossier - Valid (should return 201)
# Replace <JWT> with actual token from OAuth flow
# POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dossiers
# Content-Type: application/json
# Authorization: Bearer <JWT>
#
# {
#   "namespace": "yuvaldim/test",
#   "content": "---\nname: my-dossier\ntitle: My Dossier\nversion: 1.0.0\n---\n\n# Hello\n\nThis is a test dossier.",
#   "changelog": "Initial publish"
# }

###

### ========================================
### Delete Tests
### ========================================

### Delete Dossier - No Token (should return 401 MISSING_TOKEN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dossiers/test-org/my-dossier

###

### Delete Dossier - Invalid Token (should return 401 INVALID_TOKEN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dossiers/test-org/my-dossier
Authorization: Bearer invalid.token.here

###

### Delete Dossier - Not Found (should return 404)
# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dossiers/nonexistent/dossier
# Authorization: Bearer <JWT>

###

### Delete Dossier - Wrong namespace (should return 403 FORBIDDEN)
# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dossiers/someone-else/my-dossier
# Authorization: Bearer <JWT>

###

### Delete Dossier - Valid (should return 200)
# Replace <JWT> with actual token from OAuth flow
# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dossiers/yuvaldim/test/my-dossier
# Authorization: Bearer <JWT>

###

### Delete Dossier - Specific Version (should return 200)
# Replace <JWT> with actual token from OAuth flow
# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dossiers/yuvaldim/test/my-dossier?version=1.0.0
# Authorization: Bearer <JWT>

###

### Delete Dossier - Wrong Version (should return 404 VERSION_NOT_FOUND)
# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dossiers/yuvaldim/test/my-dossier?version=99.0.0
# Authorization: Bearer <JWT>
